original_title: PFL Playoffs 2019 - PFL 7: Michaud vs. Franca
overview: The PFL 7 mixed martial arts event for the 2019 season of the Professional Fighters League was held on October 11, 2019, at the Mandalay Bay Events Center in Las Vegas, Nevada. Kayla Harrison was initially scheduled to face Genah Fabian at this event. However, Fabian missed weight and was replaced by Bobbi-Jo Dalziel.
title: PFL Playoffs 2019 - PFL 7: Michaud vs. Franca
